Core Features:
Session Management
Chat interface for therapy sessions
Message history display
Message input and sending
Real-time message updates
Session status indicators (active/ended)
Recommendations System
Display current recommendations
Feedback buttons (thumbs up/down)
Loading states during pattern analysis (~5.3s as seen in logs)
Update notifications when new recommendations arrive
History of past recommendations
Emotional Progress Tracking
Display emotional trends
Progress indicators
Recurring themes visualization
Key emotions and their triggers
User Profile
Basic user info
Session history
Check-in status
Emotional profile summary




